[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: the care team has no visibility into the assistant's activity, the assistant operates as a parallel system rather than as an extension of the care team, the outcome-correlation evidence is missing when leadership asks for it, the equity-disparity findings are not surfaced, and the protocol-revision feedback loop does not close. Care-team reporting is not a phase-2 enhancement; it is the operating-room visibility that makes the assistant a tool the care team trusts.
