[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2347[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The conversation has been documented; the patient was
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2348[0m:[38;5;10m[49m told to remain on the discharge dose until the dose is
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2349[0m:[38;5;10m[49m confirmed, with the alternative path of staying on the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2350[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 60 mg dose if the wife is confident in the source. The
